{"tid":132522,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"自從我轉左中移動 我人生有左翻天覆既改變","createTime":"2017-02-24T01:37:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-26T08:18:45.000Z","uid":56524,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"44dceaabcf57218b8c71d25fa6e208c7232b5e61","tid":132522,"uid":56524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T01:37:50.000Z","msg":"從前既我日日返工成隻死狗咁<br />\n<br />\n女同事見到我就覺得我好口臭<br />\n<br />\n每日去到三點鐘就眼訓到仆街<br />\n<br />\n諗住去廁所補補眠都會俾manager估到<br />\n<br />\n又屌我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我覺得自我形象好低 好廢 好冇工作能力<br />\n<br />\n我諗唔到我有咩方法可以改變現狀<br />\n<br />\n但係自從用左中國移動之後<br />\n<br />\n我開始養成左返工搭地鐵果一個鐘地鐵全程訓足既習慣<br />\n<br />\n返到office果刻個人已經入晒狀態<br />\n<br />\n仲識得同人say good morning<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n講句野都聲如洪鐘 對眼厲人果下直情好似house of cards個 kevin spacey咁<br />\n<br />\nD女同事成日借d兒問下係味體力好好 有冇跑開馬拉松<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n中國移動<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我屌你老母咩一入地鐵就load空氣 淨係識9吹加緊乜乜77改善緊<br />\n<br />\n改你老豆咩?? 改左去邊呀??<br />\n<br />\n仆你個街我而家日日成個傻仔咁等個page load, 等到等唔到就訓教<br />\n<br />\n成日驚後而d師奶會笑9我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n屌!!!"},{"pid":"535720dda9d5c387fbc59e4b5ecd095146903925","tid":132522,"uid":8334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T01:41:06.000Z","msg":"難度你就覺得連登仔唔會笑鳩你? <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c32c36432df853f867f571cc75fbaf29929dd1bf","tid":132522,"uid":52194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T01:42:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\