2-26T03:07:13.000Z","msg":"以前係地鐵上舊登,load個page load成幾分鐘,load到成條綠色線都搭完都係睇得幾版,一完約即刻射個三分波轉台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 依加唔好講睇連登,係地鐵睇YouTube都快如閃電<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申:smartone<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f00dbeabef89a56aba6385b14bad8e57bfb2e20","tid":132522,"uid":54481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T03:10:42.000Z","msg":"冇錯！一齊沽爆中移動！"},{"pid":"d1321dc7a30853096ea516c0049a9f21b5d4dc8f","tid":132522,"uid":6347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T03:13:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04e368ea1e97f1373122b6b03af71d2f5e0b8c8d","tid":132522,"uid":56524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T08:18:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/26/161842_16720d55650f55372e2e46daa9c31dc8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F26%2F161842_16720d55650f55372e2e46daa9c31dc8.jpg&h=da11d0f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「訊號零格，都唔係一次！」中移動下午發生故障，用戶的電話沒有訊號及網絡。這是中移動兩個半月內第二次故障，網民嬲爆在fb專頁「洗版」表達不滿！<br />\n<br />\n下午近2時，多名中移動用戶，發現手機完全沒有訊號，與今年1月故障時，出現的狀況一樣，有人「傾傾吓電話無訊號！」致電客戶查詢熱線又接不通，感到非常激氣，紛紛在中移動的fb專頁表達不滿。<br />\n<br />\n至下午3時04分，中移動在其fb專頁解釋，是由於電力配套故障，導致客戶嘅數據及話音服務可能受到影響，並盡力搶修，對受影響客戶深表抱歉。<br />\n<br />\n今年1月4日中午時份，中移動亦因出現電力配套故障問題，引致部分客戶的話音及流動數據服務受到影響，搶修逾3小時始陸續恢復正常。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170226&amp;guid=56356106&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170226%26guid%3D56356106%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant&d=Xx1rX%2BBWBBKZa4OSQyufSYzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=639a6712\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170226%26guid%3D56356106%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant&h=192ee222\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170226&amp;guid=56356106&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant</a>"}]}